  "texts": [
    "-Created a model, MCCM which is composed of two classifiers, each of which corresponds to a sensitive attribute, e.g., male or female.",
    "-Used Rawlsian Fairness, LR, Learning Fair Representation, and Adversarial Learned Fair Representation as baselines.",
    "Accuracy, Discrimination and Consistency.",
    "The proposed model MCCM recorded the best performance in mitigating bias in terms of discrimination.",
    "Though designed for individual fairness, the proposed MCCM achieved both group fairness and individual fairness, because group and individual fairness are highly correlated."
